item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Emmy Rossum "Inside Out Documentary (Long Version)" Video
item.description:
Hi,

I've been looking for this very rare video for a very long time, but seeing what incredible content this website has, I decided to try to find it here. It was originally included in the EP version of the album "Inside Out" available on the Itunes store, but now it has mysteriously disappeared from it. The only version of this video I've found is available on Dailymotion, but it is highly compressed and with distorted audio, it's very bad.

A huge thank you in advance
